hadiths[34]{hadithnumber,text}:
3893,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nek aadmi ka achchha khuwab nabuwat ka chhiyaaliswan hissa hai.
3894,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin ka khuwab nabuwat ka chhiyaaliswan hissa hai."
3895,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman nek aadmi ka khuwab nabuwat key sattar hisson mein sey eik hissa hai."
3896,"Hazrat Umme Kurz Kaabiyaa‬ (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nabuwat khatam ho gaee aur khushkhabri deney wali cheezen reh gaeen, yani sachhey khuwab baqi hain."
3897,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : achchha khuwab nabuwat ka sattarwaan hissa hai."
3898,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit‬ (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey Allah Taala key is farman key mutalliq daryaft kiya : (لَهُمُ الْبُشْرَى فِي الْحَيَاةِ الدُّنْيَا وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ),""un key liye duniya ki zindagi mein bhi khushkhabri hai aur aakhirat mein bhi.'' to aap ney farmaya : is sey murad achchha khuwab hai jo musalman dekhta hai, ya uskey liye dekha jata hai."
3899,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney (aakhiri) marz key dinon mein (eik din) parda hataayaa jabkey log Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey safein baandhey huye (namaz padh rahey) they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logo ! nabuwat ki khush khabri deney wali chizon mein sey sirf nek khuwab baqi hain jisey koi musalman dekhta hai, ya uskey liye dekha jata hai."
3900,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney mujhey khuwab mein dekha, usney (goya) mujhey bedaari mein dekha kyonkey shetan meri surat ikhtiyar nahin kar sakta."
3901,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney khuwab mein mujhey dekha , usney mujhey hi dekha kyonkey shetan meri surat ikhtiyar nahin kar sakta."
3902,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney khuwab mein mujhey dekha , usney mujhey hi dekha. shetan is qabil nahin ke meri surat ikhtiyar kerey."
3903,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney khuwab mein mujhey dekha, usney mujhey hi dekha kyonkey shetan meri surat ikhtiyar nahin kar sakta."
3904,"Hazrat Abu-Juhaifa Wahab bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney mujhey khuwab mein dekha , goya usney mujhey bedaari mein dekha. shetan ye taqat nahin rakhta ke meri surat ikhtiyar kerey."
3905,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney mujhey khuwab mein dekha , usney mujhey dekha kyonkey shetan meri surat ikhtiyar nahin kar sakta."
3906,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khuwab teen qism key hotey hain : (eik) Allah ki taraf sey khush khabri, (doosrey) dil key khayalat aur (teesrey) shetan ki taraf sey khof-zada karney key liye (burey aur daraawne khuwab). jab kisi ko aisa khuwab aaye jo usey achchha lagey to agar wo chahey to usey (kisi key samney) bayan kar dey. aur agar koi naa-pasandida chiz nazar aaye to kisi ko khuwab na sunaiye aur uth kar namaz padhey."
3907,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khuwab teen qism key hotey hain : baaz khuwab daraawne hotey hain, (wo) shetan ki taraf sey insan ko pareshan karney key liye (hotey hain). baaz aisey hotey hain ke insan bedaari ki haalat mein jo kuch sochta rehta hai, wohi kuchh khuwab mein usey nazar aa jata hai. aur baaz (khuwab) wo hain jo nabuwat ka chhiyaaliswan hissa hain. Hazrat Muslim bin Mushkim (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : kya aap ney ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (baraahe-raast) suni hai? Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : haan, mainey ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey khud suni hai. haan, mainey ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey khud suni hai."
3908,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ko aisa khuwab aaye jo usey bura lagey to usey chahiye ke baain taraf teen baar thook dey, aur teen baar shetan sey Allah ki panah maangey, aur jis pehlu par letaa huwa ho usey badal dey (doosrey pehlu par let kar so jaey)."
3909,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : achcha khuwab Allah ki taraf sey hota hai aur bura khuwab shetan ki taraf sey, isliye agar kisi ko (khuwab mein) aisi chiz nazar aaye jo usey nagawar ho to usey chahiye ke teen baar baain taraf thook dey aur shetan mardud sey teen baar Allah ki panah maangey, aur jis pehlu par letaa huwa ho usey badal dey."
3910,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ko aisa khuwab aaye jo usey bura lagey to usey chahiye ke karwat badal ley aur baain taraf teen baar thook dey. aur Allah Taala sey is khuwab ki behtari ka sawal karey aur iskey shar sey (Allah ki) panah maangey."
3911,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : mainey (khuwab mein) dekha ke mera sar uda diya gaya hai. mainey dekha ke wo ludhaktaa ja raha hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shetan (baaz oqaat) kisi insan ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar usey (khuwab mein) khof-zada karta hai, phir wo (shakhs) subah logon ko bataaney lagta hai (ye munasib nahin)."
3912,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farma rahey they ke eik aadmi aaya aur usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aaj raat mainey khuwab mein dekha ke mera gala kaat diya gaya hai aur mera sar (jism sey alag ho kar) gir gaya hai. mainey us (ludakte huye sar) ka taaqqub (peechha) kar key usey pakad liya aur dobara (jism par) laga liya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi key sath shetan khuwab mein shararat kerey. to wo (ye khuwab) logon ko hergiz na bataey."
3913,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ko (bura) khuwab aaye to usey chahiye ke khuwab mein us sey honey wali shetani sharaarten logon ko na bataey."
3914,"Hazrat Abu-Rizeen (Laqeet bin Sabra Uqeli) (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke be-shak unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : khuwab ki jab tak tabeer bayan na ki jaey us waqt tak wo (goya) perindey key paon mein hota hai. jab tabeer kar di jaey to waqey ho jata hai. aur farmaya : khuwab nabuwat key chhiyaalees hisson mein sey eik hissa hai. aur ghaaliban ye bhi farmaya : khuwab sirf usi ko sunaiye jo mohabbat rakhney wala ya samajhdaar ho."
3915,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khuwabon ko un (mein nazar aaney wali chizon) key namon sey samjho, aur chizon ki kunniyaton sey unkey kinayo (aur ishaaron) ko samjho, aur khuwab pehley tabeer karney waley key liye hai."
3916,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney jhoota khuwab bayan kiya usey jau key do daanon ko eik doosrey sey gireh laganey ka hukm diya jaaeyga aur (wo aisa nahin kar sakeyga, chunanche) usey is wajeh sey azab diya jaeyga."
3917,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab zamana (khatam honey key) qarib aa jaeyga to (us zamaney mein) momin ka khuwab bahut hi kam jhoot niklega. aur ziyada sachcha khuwab uska hoga jo (roz marra zindagi mein) baat cheet mein ziyada sachcha hai. aur momin ka khuwab nabuwat key chhiyaalees hisson mein sey eik hissa hai."
3918,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jange-ohad sey wapis tashrif laye to eik aadmi aap ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey khuwab main eik sayeban (ya badal) dekha hai jis sey ghi aur shehad tapak raha tha. aur mainey dekha ke log us (ghi aur shehad) sey ley rahey hain. koi ziyada ley raha hai koi kam. aur mainey eik rassi dekhi jo aasman tak pahunchi hui thi. aur mainey dekha ke aap ney isey pakda aur uskey zariey sey ooper tashrif ley gaey, phir aap key baad eik aur aadmi ney wo rassi pakdi aur wo uskey zariey sey ooper chala gaya, phir uskey baad eik aur aadmi ney isey pakda wo bhi uskey zariey sey ooper chala gaya, phir uskey baad eik aadmi ney isey pakda to wo toot gaee. phir wo rassi jod di gaee to wo uskey zariey sey ooper chala gaya. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey iski tabeer karney ki ijazat dijiye . aap ney farmaya : aap iski tabeer karen. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : sayeban (ya badal) to Islam hai. us sey tapakney wala shehad aur ghi Quran, yani uski mithaas aur narmi hai, aur us sey leney waley log kam ya ziyada Quran (ka ilm aur samajh) hasil karney waley hain. aasman tak pahunchney wali rassi sey murad wo haq (sachcha deen) hai jis par aap qaaim hain. aap ney isey pakda aur uskey zariey sey buland ho gaey (buland darjaat par faaiz ho gaey). phir aap key baad eik aadmi pakdeyga aur uskey zariey sey buland ho jaeyga. phir doosra aadmi bhi us (ko pakad kar us) key zariey sey buland ho jaeyga. phir eik aur aadmi pakdeyga to rassi toot jaeygi lekin phir jud jaaeygi aur wo uskey zariey sey buland ho jaeyga. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aap ney kuchh sahih kaha aur kuchh ghalati ki hai. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah key Rasool ! main aap ko qism dey kar arz karta hun ke mujhey ye bata dijiye ke mainey kon si baat sahih kahi aur kon si ghalat kahi. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Abu-Bakar ! qism na khaao. dusri sanad mein Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey marvi hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they ke eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey aasman aur zamin key darmiyan eik sayeban (ya badal) dekha jis sey ghi aur shehad tapak raha tha-----  .,  aur puri hadees (matlab ke aetibaar se) pehli hadees ki maanind bayan ki."
3919,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein ghair shaadi shuda nojawan ladka tha. main raat ko masjid mein soyaa karta tha. hum mein sey jo koi khuwab dekhta , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan karta. mainey kaha : ya Allah ! agar terey paas merey liye khair hai to mujhey bhi koi khuwab dikha dey jiski tabeer Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) keren, chunanche (eik baar) main soyaa to mainey (khuwab mein) dekha ke merey paas do farishtey aaye aur mujhey sath ley gaey. unhen eik aur farishta mila, usney (mujh sey) kaha : ghabra mat. wo dono farishtey mujhey jahannam ki taraf ley gaey. dekha to uski mundair bani hui thi jis tarah kunwen ki mundair hoti hai. mainey dekha ke is mein kuch log they jin mein sey baaz ko mainey pehchan liya, phir wo (farishtey) mujhey daain taraf ley gaey. subah hui to mainey ye khuwab (apni hamsheera Ummul-mominin) Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ko sunaya. Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney bataya ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye khuwab sunaya to aap ney farmaya : Abdullah nek aadmi hai, kaash! wo raat ko Namaze-Tahajjud ziyada padhta. (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) key betey Hazrat Salim (Rahimahullah) ney) farmaya : isliye Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) raat ko bahut ziyada namaz padhtey they."
3920,"Hazrat Khadsha bin Harfzaari (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Madina Munawra aaya to Masjide-Nabawi mein kuchh buzurg hazraat key paas beth gaya. eik buzurg lathi tekte tashrif laye to logon ney kaha : jo koi eik jannati aadmi ko dekhna chahta hai, wo unhen dekh ley. unhoney eik sutoon key peechhey khadey ho kar do rakat namaz padhi. main uth kar unkey paas gaya aur unhen kaha : kuchh log aap key barey mein is tarah kehtey hain. unhoney kaha : Alhamdulillah ! jannat Allah ki hai, wo jisey chahega is mein dakhil kerega. (log ye baat isliye kehtey hain ke) mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamana Mubarak main eik khuwab dekha tha. mainey dekha goya eik aadmi merey paas aaya aur usney kaha : chaley to main uskey sath chal pada. wo mujhey eik badi shah-raah par ley chala. (chaltey-chaltey) mujhey baain taraf eik raasta nazar aaya. mainey is par chalney ka irada kiya to us (merey sathi) ney kaha : aap is raastey walon mein sey nahin. phir mujhey daain taraf eik raasta nazar aaya. main is par chal pada yahan tak key main eik phisalwan pahad tak ja pahuncha. us shakhs ney mera haath pakda aur mujhey ooper ki taraf uchhaal diya. achcha main us (pahad) ki choti par pahunch gaya. main wahan na thehar saka aur paon na jama saka. achcha dekha ke lohey ka eik sutoon hai jis key baalaai hissey mein soney ka eik halqa hai. us shakhs ney mera haath pakda aur mujhey ooper uchhaal diya yahan tak key mainey wo halqa pakad liya. usney kaha : kya aap ney isey achchhi tarah pakad liya hai? mainey kaha : haan, to phir usney sutoon ko paon maara (aur gira diya) aur main halqey ko mazbooti sey pakdey raha (phir main bedaar ho gaya). Sahaba farmatey hain : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khuwab sunaya to aap ney farmaya : tu ney achchhi chiz dekhi hai. wo shah-raah to maidane mehshar thi. baain taraf jo raasta nazar aaya, wo jahannamiyon ka raasta tha. to us raastey walon mein sey nahin. aur jo raasta tujhey daain taraf nazar aaya, wo ehale-jannat ka raasta tha. wo phisalwan pahad shaheedon ka maqam tha aur jo halqa tu ney pakda wo Islam ka halqa hai. usey faut honey tak mazbooti sey pakdey rehna. (ab us khuwab aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki us tabeer ki wajeh sey) mujhey ummid hai ke main jannat walon mein sey hunga. (daryaft karney par) malum huwa ke wo Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) they."
3921,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey khuwab mein dekha ke main Makka sey aisey ilaqey ki taraf hijrat kar raha hun jahan khajuron key darkht (bahut ziyada) hain. mujhey khayal aaya ke wo Yamaama ya Hijr ka ilaaqa hai. lekin wo to Madina, yani Yasrib tha. aur mainey apney us khuwab mein dekha ke mainey talwaar chalai to uska aglaa hissa toot gaya. uska matlab (ye zahir huwa ke wo) Uhud key din musalmanon ko pahunchney wala nuqsan tha, phir mainey talwaar ko harkat di to wo pehley sey behtar ho gaee. to us sey murad wo Fateh aur musalmanon ka (muntashir ho janey key baad) ikhatta ho jana tha jo Allah ney nasib farmaya. mainey us khuwab mein gaayen dekhin aur (khuwab mein suna) Allah behtari wala hai. uska matlab jange-uhad mein shaheed honey waley momin afrad they. aur khair sey murad baad mein hasil honey wali bhalai thi (aur is sey pehley) Badr mein Allah ney hamein khulus ka jo sawab ata farmaya (wo murad tha)."
3922,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey apney haathon mein soney key do kangan dekhey. mainey un par phunk maari (to wo ghaaieb ho gaey). mainey uski tabeer ki ke un sey murad ye do kazaab (jhoote) hain : Musailma aur Ansiyaa."
3923,"Hazrat Qaabus bin Makhaariq (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat Umme Fazal (Lubaaba binte Haris) (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey (khuwab mein) dekha goya merey ghar mein aap key jism Mubarak ka hissa hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tu ney achchhi chiz dekhi hai. Fatima (Raziallahu anha) key yahan ladka paida hoga to tum usey doodh pilaogi. chunanche Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) key yahan Hazrat Hasan ya Hazrat Husain (Raziallahu anhuma) ki wiladat hui to unhen Umme Al-Fazal (Raziallahu anha) ney doodh pilaya jo Qu'sam (bin Abbas) (Raziallahu anhu) sey tha. unhoney bayan farmaya : main unhen (Hasan ya Husain (Raziallahu anhuma) ko) ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur aap ke aaghosh mein rakh diya. bachchey ney peshab kar diya to mainey uskey kandhey par chapat lagai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah tujh par reham karey ! tu ney merey betey ko takleef pahunchaai hai."
3924,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khuwab bayan farmaya ke aap ney farmaya : mainey eik siyah faam aur bikhrey baalon wali aurat dekhi, wo Madina sey nikli aur mehyaa, yani Johfa key maqam par ja thehri. mainey uski tabeer ye ki ke Madina ki wabaa Johfa muntaqil ho gaee hai."
3925,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qabila Balli key do aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas (hijrat kar key Madina) aagaey. wo dono ikhattey musalman huye they. un mein sey eik doosrey ki nisbat (neki key kamon mein) ziyada mehnat karney wala tha, chunanche us mehnat karney waley ney jihad kiya aur shaheed ho gaya. doosra aadmi uskey baad eik saal tak zinda raha, phir wo faut ho gaya. Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey khuwab mein dekha ke main jannat key darwazey par khada hun. achcha dekha ke wo dono bhi wahan mojud hain. jannat sey eik aadmi bahar aaya aur usney baad mein faut honey waley ko (jannat mein janey ki) ijazat dey di. (kuchh der baad) wo phir nikla aur shaheed honey waley ko ijazat dey di. phir meri taraf mutawajjeh ho kar kaha : wapis chaley jao, abhi aap ka waqt nahin aaya. subah hui to Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney logon ko khuwab sunaya. unhen is par tajjub huwa . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bhi malum huwa , aur logon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (tafsil sey khuwab ki) baat sunai. aap ney farmaya : tumhen kis baat par tajjub hai? unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! dono mein ye shakhs ziyada mehnat wala tha, phir usey shahadat bhi nasib hui lekin jannat mein doosra is sey pehley chala gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye (doosra) us (pehley) key baad eik saal tak zinda nahin raha? unhoney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : usney Ramzan ka mahina paya aur is mein rozey rakhey aur saal mein itni itni rakat namaz padhi? unhoney kaha : ji haan. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : un dono (key darjaat) main to aasman aur zamin key darmiyani fasley sey bhi ziyada farq hai."
3926,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main toq ko napasand karta hun aur (paaon ki) bedi ko pasand karta hun. bedi Deen mein sabit qadmi ki alamat hai."
